snippet.title: Perpetuum - Launch Trailer [HD]
snippet.description:
http://www.perpetuum-online.com - Sci-Fi MMO - Release: 2010/11/25

The launch trailer for the new science fiction MMORPG Perpetuum.
Perpetuum will be launched on the 25th of November 2010, with early access starting on the 18th of November. Early access subscriptions are available on the website until the 16th of November for  €8.95/$9.95 depending on the region.

All the material in the trailer is undoctored ingame footage.
